<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA524_01_SU_0003_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema524_common.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/css/ema524_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema524_01_su_0003">
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-type="1" data-text="자기주도 2">
          <span class="blue line" lang="y">배운 내용을 떠올려요</span>
          <span lang="y">카드를 선택하여 이전에 배운 내용을 확인해 봅시다.</span>
        </h2>
      </section>


      <section class="contents">
        <ul class="letCheck">
          <li>
            <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
            <div class="front">
              <p class="f32b" lang="y">분수와 소수 사이의 관계<br>알아보기</p>
            </div>
            <div class="back">
              <p class="f32b flex align_center"><span class="fraction_box"><span>4</span><span>10</span></span> &equals; 0.4</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
            <div class="front">
              <p class="f32b" lang="y">소수 사이의 관계<br>알아보기</p>
            </div>
            <div class="back">
              <p class="f32b flex gap_40">
                <span class="arrow_box">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA524_01_SU/0003_arrow01.png" alt="arrow left">
                  <span><span class="fraction_box small"><span>1</span><span>10</span></span>배</span>
                </span>
                <span class="arrow_box">
                  <img src="../../common_contents/img/EMA524_01_SU/0003_arrow02.png" alt="arrow right">
                  <span><span>10</span>배</span>
                </span>
                <span>0.047</span><span>0.47</span><span>4.7</span>
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
            <div class="front">
              <p class="f32b" lang="y">소수의 덧셈과 뺄셈하기</p>
            </div>
            <div class="back">
              <p class="f32b">0.35&plus;2.7&equals;3.05</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li>
            <div class="cover pointer large"></div>
            <div class="front">
              <p class="f32b" lang="y">(분수)×(자연수),<br>(자연수)×(분수)<br>알아보기</p>
            </div>
            <div class="back">
              <p class="f32b">   
                <div class="flex dir_col align_center" lang="y">
                  <div class="f32b flex align_center">
                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>16</span></span>×4&equals;
                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>3</span><span>4</span></span>,
                  </div>
                  <div class="f32b flex align_center">
                    4×1<span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span>&equals;5
                    <span class="fraction_box"><span>1</span><span>3</span></span> 
                    <div class="pare_wrap">
                      &equals;<span class="fraction_box"><span>16</span><span>3</span></span>
                    </div>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ul>

        <div class="bubble_charactor" data-charactor="1" style="display: none;">
          <div class="bubble" data-point-position="bottom left">
              <p lang="y">카드를 한 번 더 선택하면</p>
              <p lang="y">내용을 볼 수 있어요.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
